All existing records possessed by the Federal Emergency Management Agency (“FEMA”) in relation to and sufficient to identify the “FEMA contractor” referred to in the September 3, 2019 letter from FEMA to Ruth Luwish (enclosed) regarding a privacy incident involving FEMA’s overshare of disaster survivor information with a contractor that supports FEMA’s Transitional Sheltering Assistance program.
